<style>
  body[data-page="blog"] .blog-grid {
    max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 28px;
  }
  .blog-card {
    text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 28px; transition: transform .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: rgba(185,143,255,0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px -16px rgba(185,143,255,0.30);
  }
  .blog-card-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
    font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #b98fff; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .blog-card-eyebrow::before { content: ""; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 999px; background: #b98fff; }
  .blog-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.18;
    color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .blog-card-lede {
    font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-dim); margin: 0 0 22px; flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .blog-card-meta {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .blog-card-readtime { text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 600; }
  .blog-card-arrow { color: #b98fff; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body data-page="blog">

<div class="ambient"></div>
<div class="grain"></div>

<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute" aria-hidden="true">
  <defs>
    <symbol id="i-logo" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="2,22 7.6,4 12,15 16.4,2 22,22"/></symbol>
    <symbol id="i-arrow-up-right" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="7" y1="17" x2="17" y2="7"/><polyline points="7 7 17 7 17 17"/></symbol>
    <symbol id="i-menu" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></symbol>
    <symbol id="i-edit" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 1 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></symbol>
  </defs>
</svg>

<div id="nav-mount"></div>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="section-eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>Field notes</div>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title reveal">Notes from<br>the <em>trading floor.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-lede reveal">
    Market commentary, data deep-dives, and stories from the people building the exchange for culture. Read about the artists moving the market, the data behind the prices, and how streaming is reshaping what an artist is "worth."
  </p>
</section>

<section class="block">
  <div class="blog-grid">

    <a class="blog-card reveal" href="/blog/what-is-a-stock-market-for-artists">
      <div class="blog-card-eyebrow">Foundations</div>
      <h3>What is a stock market for artists?</h3>
      <p class="blog-card-lede">A plain-language explainer for the concept Muses is built on — what it means to "invest" in an artist, how the prices work, and what makes it different from real investing.</p>
      <div class="blog-card-meta">
        <span class="blog-card-readtime">7 min read</span>
        <span class="blog-card-arrow">Read &rarr;</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="blog-card reveal" href="/blog/how-spotify-streams-translate-to-artist-value">
      <div class="blog-card-eyebrow">Methodology</div>
      <h3>How Spotify streams translate to artist "value"</h3>
      <p class="blog-card-lede">Streams are the music industry's most-quoted number, but they don't translate to artist value in a straight line. Here's how the formula works and why every piece of it exists.</p>
      <div class="blog-card-meta">
        <span class="blog-card-readtime">8 min read</span>
        <span class="blog-card-arrow">Read &rarr;</span>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="block">
  <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center; max-width:640px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:36px; margin:0 0 14px;">More posts<br>are on the way.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink-dim); margin:0 0 24px;">New articles weekly. Get the next one in your inbox the day it goes live.</p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/waitlist">Join the waitlist <svg><use href="#i-arrow-up-right"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn-ghost" href="/exchange">Launch app</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="footer-mount"></div>

<script src="muse-shared.js?v=20260427a"></script>
</body>
</html>
